Package polyglot.ast

Interface DelFactory

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractDelFactory_c
@Deprecated
public interface DelFactory
Deprecated.
A DelFactory constructs delegates. It is only used by a NodeFactory, during the creation of AST nodes.
